{"tid":736181,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"女團TWICE夏日熱曲登頂韓6大音樂榜","createTime":"2018-07-10T05:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T09:16:50.000Z","uid":51412,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f68b0ded120ef19cfebcd703d0bba214e78c508f","tid":736181,"uid":51412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T05:09:12.000Z","msg":"韓聯社首爾7月10日電截至10日上午7時，韓國人氣女團TWICE前一日下午6時公開的特別二輯《Summer Nights》主題曲《Dance The Night Away》登頂Melon、Genie、Mnet MUSIC 、Soribada等6個音源榜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.yonhapnews.co.kr/etc/inner/CK/2018/07/10/ACK20180710000400881_02_i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.yonhapnews.co.kr%2Fetc%2Finner%2FCK%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2FACK20180710000400881_02_i.jpg&h=b92cde0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由此，繼《CHEER UP》《TT》《KNOCK KNOCK》《SIGNAL》《LIKEY》《HEART SHAKER》《What is love?》後，TWICE發布的9首歌皆登頂韓國主流音樂榜，驗證其超高人氣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.yonhapnews.co.kr/etc/inner/CK/2018/07/10/ACK20180710000400881_03_i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.yonhapnews.co.kr%2Fetc%2Finner%2FCK%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2FACK20180710000400881_03_i.jpg&h=56eeb534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《Summer Nights》收錄包括《Dance The Night Away》《CHILLAX》《Shot thru the heart》共三首新歌。《Dance The Night Away》著重描寫9位成員的青春魅力，由歌手輝星作詞，充滿休閒的夏日度假氛圍。值得一提的是，日籍成員Momo、Sana、Mina還參與了《Shot thru the heart》的作詞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.yonhapnews.co.kr/etc/inner/CK/2018/07/10/ACK20180710000400881_04_i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.yonhapnews.co.kr%2Fetc%2Finner%2FCK%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2FACK20180710000400881_04_i.jpg&h=b432ae4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日籍成員Mina<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.yonhapnews.co.kr/etc/inner/CK/2018/07/10/ACK20180710000400881_05_i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.yonhapnews.co.kr%2Fetc%2Finner%2FCK%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2FACK20180710000400881_05_i.jpg&h=5bf0c573&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日籍成員Sana<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.yonhapnews.co.kr/etc/inner/CK/2018/07/10/ACK20180710000400881_06_i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.yonhapnews.co.kr%2Fetc%2Finner%2FCK%2F2018%2F07%2F10%2FACK20180710000400881_06_i.jpg&h=b0c77e70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日籍成員Momo<br />\n<br />\n另外，TWICE在結束國內活動後，將於9月12日在日本推出首張正規專輯《BDZ》。"},{"pid":"ca074d8f0cc8bb9b4ce99413a21ff97efb9d8a5a","tid":736181,"uid":51412,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:16:50.000Z","msg":"推"}]}